{"tid":1093772,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點解咁既男仔都會有女朋友","createTime":"2019-04-05T20:45:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-08T10:24:21.000Z","uid":238543,"like":46,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bf6d772d0b9b1b7f308ffe5286e82c966bbdb0","tid":1093772,"uid":238543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T20:45:57.000Z","msg":"公司同事<br />\n雖然生得高<br />\n但真心好撚肥<br />\n樣衰矇豬眼<br />\n<br />\n講嘢好撚低能<br />\n成個小學雞咁<br />\n又鍾意係公司扮大佬以為自己好叻<br />\n全公司冇一個人妥佢<br />\n得閒冇事做就鍾意拎部手機<br />\n出來偷拍同事醜態放上group笑鳩人<br />\n心地差到極點<br />\n<br />\n工作又唔係特別認真<br />\n成日遲到<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明廿幾歲人咁on鳩都會有女<br />\n連登巴打好過佢多多聲<br />\n<br />\n重點係佢女朋友睇落都唔差<br />\n係啲偽ABC樣來<br />\n細細粒<br />\n條女究竟係冇腦定同佢一樣咁低質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：有同朋友講果下呢條白癡仔，勿相認"},{"pid":"0ffd8ffb3f56eb54d0d905010af9b7f6d696a054","tid":1093772,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-05T21:14:09.000Z","msg":"蔫豬頭有盲鼻菩薩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f614abd1c78c8832db84b83c109061e9304671e9","tid":1093772,"uid":219081,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:13:48.000Z","msg":"因為女人多 on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed997e4c3abe3dab2adb99ebb17f8b613dc6d4e","tid":1093772,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:16:39.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"c4c9c328b97627599be8383fcde181a6c519ed82","tid":1093772,"uid":66099,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:16:56.000Z","msg":"你再噉多事我就叫uncle炒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a1d7a8b2365c45e94be612c49d98ccac579ca8b","tid":1093772,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"$"},{"pid":"e7eec83f1cbcc6f72ac282672f72f01440805db5","tid":1093772,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited